- "spreading digital weeds" refers to users who have been blocked for spamming comments;
- "messages" refers to the content of the comments;
- "day they were silenced" refers to the date the block was created.

- "blossoms" refers to users;
- "type" refers to the user role (user, moderator, admin);
- "towers" refers to highly engaged users with total engagement > 1000;
- "gardeners" refers to users who have made more than 10 comments;
- "pruned their branches" refers to users who have modified their comments more than 5 times.

