- "Cut down by the gardeners of moderation" refers to comments that were rejected by moderators;
- "Branches of conversation" refers to comments and their replies.

- 'Planting seeds of conversation' refers to posting comments;
- 'Gardeners' refers to users with different roles in the system (users, moderators, admins);
